==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Dodman
<hw>Dod"man</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>A snail;
also, a snail shell; a hodmandod.</def> <mark>[Obs. or Prov.
Eng.]</mark> <rj><au>Nares.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>Any shellfish which casts its
shell, as a lobster.</def> <mark>[Prov. Eng.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Dodo</ent>⟦br⟧
